                <h1>USABILITY ANALYSIS AND INTERACTION DESIGN</h1>
                <p>I believe that as a developer I not only have to improve my technical skills, I also believe that <strong>we work for people and we must understand our users</strong>, how they work, what they need and how we can help them develop software.</p>
                <p><strong>Since 2014</strong> I've been thinking more about <strong>usability and interaction design</strong>, or how people interact with machines. So when I'm designing and developing software I'm thinking about how I can reduce friction between the UI and the user.</p>
            </header>
